Titanium Mobile 1.7.2 - 07/20/2011
==================================

This release candidate includes general bug fixes for Android and iPhone.
Please see the updated [Titanium Mobile Reference Documentation for 1.7.2](/apidoc/mobile/1.7.2) 

[Full list of Issues that were addressed in 1.7.2](http://jira.appcelerator.org/secure/IssueNavigator.jspa?mode=hide&requestId=10946) 

Android Changes
---------------

With release 1.7.2 we support deploying applications to Honeycomb tablet devices (API 11+). Support for tablet specific controls will come in a later release.

We addressed several [issues](http://jira.appcelerator.org/secure/IssueNavigator.jspa?mode=hide&requestId=10945), including: 

- [TIMOB-4612 - Android: Reading and writing large files cause ANR / Exceptions in Fastdev](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-4612)
- [TIMOB-4527 - Android: Can't build project that has "xlarge" art in it.](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-4527)
- [TIMOB-4504 - Android: New Orientation Mechanism](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-4504)
- [TIMOB-4261 - Android tooling: Support making changes to root <activity> in <manifest> section of tiapp.xml, and having those changes be carried into generated manifest](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-4261)
- [TIMOB-4163 - Android: Debugger: Manual suspend is not implemented](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-4163)
- [TIMOB-4079 - Android: setInterval won't fire in app.js with TabGroup](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-4079)
- [TIMOB-4019 - AudioPlayer Progress is in milliseconds (iOS is Seconds)](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-4019)
- [TIMOB-3832 - Android 3.0 Xoom: date picker crashes on year change](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-3832)
- [TIMOB-3828 - Android 3.0 Xoom: Orientation - all kinds of bad behavior](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-3828)
- [TIMOB-837 - Allow multiple attachments to EmailDialog in Android](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-837)
- [TIMOB-2495 - Android: Temp files created by TiHTTPClient](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-2495)
- [TIMOB-4631 - Android: Failure to launch emulator with r12 SDK tools](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-4631)


